09/07/20,"Approval of 15% cash & 10% stock instead of 30% cash dividend The Company has further informed that as per dividend policy of Bangladesh Bank (Circular dated May 11, 2020), a bank may disburse maximum 30% total dividend out of which maximum 15% dividend may be paid in the form of cash. Accordingly, the honorable shareholders of the Bank in the 24th AGM held on July 08, 2020 has declared and approved 15% cash and 10% stock dividend instead of 30% cash Dividend for the year ended on December 31, 2019."
